            <Label alignment="CENTER" contentDisplay="CENTER" prefHeight="209.0" prefWidth="1920.0" text="Three Laws of Motion had been the backbone of Physics for centuries (up until Einstein's Theory of General Relativity). It's essential to study and understand them because they appear in everything, everywhere, everyday." textAlignment="CENTER" wrapText="true">
